going to be in that same model.

00:43:49.410 --> 00:43:50.710
It's impossible.

00:43:50.710 --> 00:43:52.010
You can't really do that.

00:43:52.010 --> 00:43:53.310
It's a bad idea.

00:43:53.310 --> 00:43:54.960
Well, I guess you can do it,
