archivists, as am I.

01:11:26.050 --> 01:11:28.840
I'm wondering, in light of the
many preservation challenges

01:11:28.840 --> 01:11:32.840
that you've outlined,
what kinds of awkward

01:11:32.840 --> 01:11:35.860
or tough conversations about
appraisal has this led to?

01:11:35.860 --> 01:11:38.370
And if you feel comfortable
offering examples,

01:11:38.370 --> 01:11:41.920
I'd love to hear about them.

