clothing at the moment.

01:11:49.280 --> 01:11:51.800
But I do have, you know,

01:11:51.800 --> 01:11:54.050
interesting conversations
about appraisal.

01:11:54.050 --> 01:11:57.390
Not probably as much as
these guys, but with one

01:11:57.390 --> 01:11:58.750
of my colleagues, Beth
Dodd [assumed spelling]

01:11:58.750 --> 01:12:00.480
at the Alexander
Architectural Archive,

01:12:00.480 --> 01:12:02.970
and we discuss frequently
some of these challenges.

01:12:02.970 --> 01:12:05.940
And I can't think of anything
specifically off the top

01:12:05.940 --> 01:12:08.300
of my head, although
we're currently --

01:12:08.300 --> 01:12:11.550
have been doing what a lot of
people are doing, is not taking

01:12:11.550 --> 01:12:14.150
in a whole lot of things as
of yet, and kind of hoping

01:12:14.150 --> 01:12:16.160
and waiting to see
what will come.

01:12:16.160 --> 01:12:19.990
We have gotten a few
collections that have, you know,

01:12:19.990 --> 01:12:21.540
a lot of digital
media, and we've had --

01:12:21.540 --> 01:12:23.810
we've been working with
students of the eye school

01:12:23.810 --> 01:12:26.760
and bringing their sort of
fresh eyes to these problems.

01:12:26.760 --> 01:12:31.490
But we are still kind of hoping
for some ways to move forward.

01:12:31.490 --> 01:12:33.280
The argument I've been
making for quite some time is

01:12:33.280 --> 01:12:35.060
that no one's going
to find a solution --

01:12:35.060 --> 01:12:37.320
no one person is going
to find a solution.

01:12:37.320 --> 01:12:40.200
No one organization is
going to find a solution,

01:12:40.200 --> 01:12:42.660
and that's one reason
we've been in conversation

01:12:42.660 --> 01:12:44.890
for quite some time, and -- I
have with others in the room,

01:12:44.890 --> 01:12:47.710
too, is I think we have
to do this collaboratively

01:12:47.710 --> 01:12:51.970
and creatively to address
both problems that Aliza

01:12:51.970 --> 01:12:53.420
and Tim just identified.

01:12:53.420 --> 01:12:56.380
And I think that's the only way
we're going to make any headway.

01:12:56.380 --> 01:12:58.790
So that's my schtick, I guess.

