that they're doing their work?

01:19:30.960 --> 01:19:34.840
And that can inform what we
choose to take on later on,

01:19:34.840 --> 01:19:36.820
and I think it is
very context-specific.

01:19:36.820 --> 01:19:39.250
Like, I think it's going to be
different in different places,

01:19:39.250 --> 01:19:42.640
