quality project going on.

01:42:29.520 --> 01:42:33.170
One thing that is very
important in the A&amp;D industry,

01:42:33.170 --> 01:42:37.240
when you talk about archival,
is the ability to verify

01:42:37.240 --> 01:42:41.700
and validate it before
you archive it, and also,

01:42:41.700 --> 01:42:44.640
the ability to verify
and validate it

01:42:44.640 --> 01:42:46.530
as you're retrieving it.

01:42:46.530 --> 01:42:50.990
