25% of the physical files

01:43:15.710 --> 01:43:19.820
that we write out in the
STEP format today are --

01:43:19.820 --> 01:43:22.170
just had to do with
verification and validation

01:43:22.170 --> 01:43:23.980
of the data that's in the file.

01:43:23.980 --> 01:43:26.340
So, like I said,
that's very important

01:43:26.340 --> 01:43:28.540
to the aerospace industry.

01:43:28.540 --> 01:43:33.520
I talked about the
model-centric data management,

01:43:33.520 --> 01:43:35.710
the model-based enterprise
a little earlier.

01:43:35.710 --> 01:43:38.780
