heavily involved with the IFC

01:43:43.440 --> 01:43:45.130
and BIM over the
years, as well --

01:43:45.130 --> 01:43:47.880
probably some of the same
people that we deal with.

01:43:47.880 --> 01:43:51.520
So it's kind of a global
community that's working

01:43:51.520 --> 01:43:57.450
on this, not just, you know,
the Boeings, and the Airbuses,

01:43:57.450 --> 01:43:58.750
and the Lockheeds of the world.

