like manufacturing does?

02:48:02.450 --> 02:48:06.370
How do we get to that
in the AEC realm?

02:48:06.370 --> 02:48:08.290
Or we will ever get there?

02:48:08.290 --> 02:48:09.590
I don't know.

02:48:09.590 --> 02:48:13.010
Does anybody want to
take a crack at that?

