02:56:17.890 --> 02:56:19.590
but sometimes maybe
you also consider

02:56:19.590 --> 02:56:22.250
that that would get copied out
to a collecting institution

02:56:22.250 --> 02:56:24.710
at some point for, like,
sort of permanent retention.

02:56:24.710 --> 02:56:26.660
